result.execSummary:
The defendant Victoria Curry was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case.

  • Disorderly Conduct [Modifiers: Party to a Crime], a class B misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 947.01(1).
  • Battery [Modifiers: Party to a Crime, Use of a Dangerous Weapon], a class A misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 940.19(1).
